### ===========================
### Service API
### ===========================

### Get all services
GET http://localhost:3000/api/services

### Create a service - 30 min consultation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "30 Min Consultation",
  "description": "Quick consultation session",
  "duration": 30,
  "price": 50
}

### Create a service - 60 min consultation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "60 Min Deep Consultation",
  "description": "In-depth consultation session",
  "duration": 60,
  "price": 100
}

### Get single service (replace SERVICE_ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/services/SERVICE_ID

### Update service (replace SERVICE_ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/services/SERVICE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "30 Min Consultation - Updated",
  "price": 60
}

### Delete service (replace SERVICE_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/services/SERVICE_ID

