### ===========================
### Booking API
### ===========================

### Get all bookings
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings

### Get bookings by user (replace USER_ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings?userId=USER_ID

### Get bookings by status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings?status=pending

### Create a booking (replace USER_ID and SERVICE_ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "USER_ID",
  "service": "SERVICE_ID",
  "date": "2025-01-20",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "09:30",
  "notes": "First consultation"
}

### Get single booking (replace BOOKING_ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/BOOKING_ID

### Update booking status (replace BOOKING_ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/BOOKING_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Delete booking (replace BOOKING_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/BOOKING_ID